with
     __dbt__cte__stg_orders as (

-- Fixture for stg_orders
select 
    
    cast(1 as INTEGER)
 as order_id, cast(null as INTEGER) as customer_id, cast(null as DATE) as order_date, cast(null as character varying(256)) as status
union all
select 
    
    cast(2 as INTEGER)
 as order_id, cast(null as INTEGER) as customer_id, cast(null as DATE) as order_date, cast(null as character varying(256)) as status
union all
select 
    
    cast(3 as INTEGER)
 as order_id, cast(null as INTEGER) as customer_id, cast(null as DATE) as order_date, cast(null as character varying(256)) as status
),  __dbt__cte__stg_payments as (

-- Fixture for stg_payments
select cast(null as INTEGER) as payment_id, 
    
    cast(1 as INTEGER)
 as order_id, 
    
    cast('credit_card' as character varying(256))
 as payment_method, 
    
    cast(10 as DOUBLE)
 as amount
union all
select cast(null as INTEGER) as payment_id, 
    
    cast(2 as INTEGER)
 as order_id, 
    
    cast('credit_card' as character varying(256))
 as payment_method, 
    
    cast(20 as DOUBLE)
 as amount
union all
select cast(null as INTEGER) as payment_id, 
    
    cast(3 as INTEGER)
 as order_id, 
    
    cast('coupon' as character varying(256))
 as payment_method, 
    
    cast(30 as DOUBLE)
 as amount
), orders as (select * from __dbt__cte__stg_orders),

    payments as (select * from __dbt__cte__stg_payments),

    order_payments as (

        select
            order_id,

            sum(
                    case
                        when payment_method = 'credit_card' then amount else 0
                    end
                ) as credit_card_amount,
            sum(
                    case
                        when payment_method = 'coupon' then amount else 0
                    end
                ) as coupon_amount,
            sum(
                    case
                        when payment_method = 'bank_transfer' then amount else 0
                    end
                ) as bank_transfer_amount,
            sum(
                    case
                        when payment_method = 'gift_card' then amount else 0
                    end
                ) as gift_card_amount,
            sum(amount) as total_amount

        from payments

        group by order_id

    ),

    final as (

        select
            orders.order_id,
            orders.customer_id,
            orders.order_date,
            orders.status,

            order_payments.credit_card_amount,

            order_payments.coupon_amount,

            order_payments.bank_transfer_amount,

            order_payments.gift_card_amount,

            order_payments.total_amount as amount

        from orders

        left join order_payments on orders.order_id = order_payments.order_id

    )

select *
from final

    payments as (select * from "dbt"."main"."stg_payments"),

        select

                    end

                    end

select coupon_amount
from "dbt"."main"."orders"
where coupon_amount is null

with all_values as (

    select
        status as value_field,
        count(*) as n_records

    from "dbt"."main"."orders"
    group by status

)

select *
from all_values
where value_field not in (
    'placed','shipped','completed','return_pending','returned'
)

select amount
from "dbt"."main"."orders"
where amount is null

select customer_id
from "dbt"."main"."orders"
where customer_id is null

select gift_card_amount
from "dbt"."main"."orders"
where gift_card_amount is null

select credit_card_amount
from "dbt"."main"."orders"
where credit_card_amount is null

select order_id
from "dbt"."main"."orders"
where order_id is null

select bank_transfer_amount
from "dbt"."main"."orders"
where bank_transfer_amount is null

select
    order_id as unique_field,
    count(*) as n_records

from "dbt"."main"."orders"
where order_id is not null
group by order_id
having count(*) > 1

with child as (
    select customer_id as from_field
    from "dbt"."main"."orders"
    where customer_id is not null
),

parent as (
    select customer_id as to_field
    from "dbt"."main"."customers"
)

select
    from_field

from child
left join parent
    on child.from_field = parent.to_field

where parent.to_field is null
